msxbas2rom (1.0.0.0-2) bionic; urgency=low

  * SET TILE FLIP and SET TILE ROTATE commands with optional bank parameter.
  * Bug fix: direction parameter was clobbered by VRAM address operations.
  * Bug fix: bank parameter was overwriting direction in 3-param compiler path.
  * Bug fix: tile rotation used sprite destination offset (STRBUF+32) instead of tile offset (STRBUF).

 -- Amaury Carvalho <amauryspires@gmail.com>  Thu, 19 Jun 2026 18:00:00 -0300

